3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The heuristic method proposed in the paper involves finding an efficient solution to a complex problem, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence research. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the computational complexity of the labeling problem and proposes a heuristic algorithm, which falls under the domain of data structures and algorithms.
